<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whichever-adj">whichever <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɪtʃ'evə(r)/    美 /wɪtʃ'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>无论哪一个 / 哪一些：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take whichever seat you like.
你喜欢哪个位子就坐哪个。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[引导让步状语从句] 不管哪个：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You will be there by 5, whichever train you take.
无论你乘坐哪趟火车，5点前都可以到那儿。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ one of you breaks the window will have to pay for it.  （2013 江西）<br />
A.Whoever<br />
B.Whatever<br />
C.whichever<br />
D.Wherever  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>